column5: Good for u, the weathermen are wimps back east, when they give the forecast from Oakville lol, I've saw one of them wear earmuffs at -2. If I can figure out how to download pics from our digital I have some showing fishing with -40 windchill, but in fairness it is much drier up here, do not feel it as much.  Good for u, winter is short, get out and enjoy it. Good looking fish.
No wonder it was cold--it's Ottawa. Lemme tell ya, the last time I was there it was so cold the politicians had their hands in their own pockets-----rah rump pa ta tum!
-42 with windchill where I was working Thursday. Supposed to be colder when I go back Sunday night.
